\sum_{x} P(x) \\log\\cfrac{P(x)}{Q(x)}$\n","<br><br>\n","$ D_{KL}(P\\|Q) = -\\displaystyle\\sum_{x} P(x) \\log\\cfrac{Q(x)}{P(x)}$\n","<br><br>\n","$\\begin{eqnarray} KL(p(x)||q(x)) & = & H(p(x), q(x)) - H(p(x))\\\\ &=& \\mathbb{E}_{p(x)}[-\\log q(x)] - \\mathbb{E}_{p(x)}[-\\log p(x)]\\\\ &=& \\mathbb{E}_{p(x)}[-\\log q(x) + \\log p(x)]\\\\ &=& \\mathbb{E}_{p(x)}\\left[\\log\\left(\\frac{p(x)}{q(x)}\\right)\\right]\\end{eqnarray}$<br><br>\n","ï¼ˆKL Divergenceï¼‰=ï¼ˆCross-Entropyï¼‰-ï¼ˆEntropyï¼‰</font><br><br>\n","- $KL(p||q) \\neq KL(q||p)$ã§ã‚ã‚Š$P$ã¨$Q$ãŒéå¯¾ç§°<br>\n","- $p(x)$ã‚’èª¿æ•´ã—ã¦ã€$p(x)$ã¨$q(x)$ã®èª¤å·®ï¼ˆã‚«ãƒ«ãƒãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒ¼æƒ…å ±é‡ï¼‰ã‚’æœ€å°åŒ–ã™ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã«ã¯ã€ç¬¬ï¼’é …ï¼ˆã‚¯ãƒ­ã‚¹ã‚¨ãƒ³ãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ”ãƒ¼ï¼‰ã‚’æœ€å°åŒ–ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã¨åŒã˜<br><br>\n","- <font color=\"silver\">JS Divergence</font><br><br>\n","$M(x) = \\cfrac{P(x)+Q(x)}{2}$<br><br>\n","$ D_{JS}(P\\|Q) = \\cfrac{1}{2}(D_{KL}(P\\|M) + D_{KL}(Q\\|M))$<br><br>\n","- $D_{KL}(P\\|M)$ã¨$D_{KL}(Q\\|M)$ã¨ã®å¹³å‡ã€å¯¾è±¡ã§äº¤æ›å¯èƒ½</font><br>\n","- çœŸã®åˆ†å¸ƒã¨å­¦ç¿’ãƒ¢ãƒ‡ãƒ«ã®åˆ†å¸ƒãŒé‡ãªã‚‰ãªã„ã¨ãã€å‹¾é…æ¶ˆå¤±å•é¡ŒãŒç”Ÿã˜ã‚‹</font><br><br>\n"],"metadata":{"id":"WssREySj2alA"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["####<font color=\"silver\">ãƒã‚¤ã‚¢ã‚¹ãƒã‚¤ãƒªã‚¢ãƒ³ã‚¹</font>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\quad$E$\\qquad$=$\\quad$ãƒã‚¤ã‚¢ã‚¹ + ãƒã‚¤ãƒªã‚¢ãƒ³ã‚¹$\\quad$+$\\qquad$ãƒã‚¤ã‚º</font><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\quad$$\\qquad$$\\qquad$$\\qquad$äºˆæ¸¬å€¤ã¨ç†æƒ³å€¤$\\qquad$+$\\qquad$ç†æƒ³å€¤ã¨å®Ÿãƒ‡ãƒ¼ã‚¿</font><br>\n","<br>\n","$\\displaystyle E\\left( L\\right) =\\int \\left\\{ y\\left( x\\right) -h\\left( x\\right) \\right\\} ^{2}p\\left( x\\right) dx + \\int \\int \\left\\{ h\\left( x\\right) -t\\right\\} ^{2}p\\left( x,t\\right) dxdy$<br><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\qquad$ãƒã‚¤ã‚¢ã‚¹$\\qquad$$\\qquad$$\\qquad$$\\qquad$+$\\qquad$$\\qquad$ãƒã‚¤ãƒªã‚¢ãƒ³ã‚¹</font><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\qquad$äºˆæ¸¬å€¤ã®æœŸå¾…å€¤ã¨ç†æƒ³å€¤$\\qquad$+$\\qquad$$\\qquad$äºˆæ¸¬å€¤ã¨äºˆæ¸¬