om/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*jxidxadWSMLvwLDZz2mycg.png\" width=\"240\">\n"," - Huber Loss\n","  - æå¤±ãŒå¤§ãã„ã¨MAEã«ä¼¼ãŸæ©Ÿèƒ½ã‚’ã—ã€æå¤±ãŒå°ã•ã„ã¨MSEã®æ©Ÿèƒ½ã«ãªã‚‹ã€‚<br>\n","  - MSEã¨MAEã®åˆ‡ã‚Šæ›¿ã‚ã‚Šã¯ğ›¿ã§è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹<br><br>\n"," - $\\rm R^2$\n","- äºˆæ¸¬ãƒ‡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã®åˆ†æ•£ãŒæ•™å¸«ãƒ‡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã®åˆ†æ•£ã«ç›¸å¯¾ã—ã¦ã€ä½•å‰²å ã‚ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã‹ã‚’è¡¨ã™ã€‚<br>\n","- ç²¾åº¦ä¾å­˜ã™ã‚‹è©•ä¾¡ã¨é•ã„ã€åˆ†æ•£ãŒä½ãã¦ã‚‚ã€ç²¾åº¦ãŒé«˜ããªã„å ´åˆãŒã‚ã‚Šå¾—ã‚‹ã€‚<br>\n","- å›å¸°åˆ†æã®å½“ã¦ã¯ã¾ã‚Šã®è‰¯ã•<br>\n","- ç›®çš„å¤‰æ•°ã®ã‚¹ã‚±ãƒ¼ãƒ«ã«ä¾å­˜ã›ãšè©•ä¾¡å¯èƒ½<br>\n","- 0ã‹ã‚‰1ã®å€¤ã‚’ã¨ã‚‹<br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\tiny\\text{ç”»åƒå¼•ç”¨å…ƒ}$[<font color=\"silver\">â€¦](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*EqTaoCB1NmJnsRYEezSACA.png)</font></font><br>\n","<img src=\"https://cor.tokyo/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88-2019-04-18-23.22.06.png\" width=\"320\"><br><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\tiny\\text{ç”»åƒå¼•ç”¨å…ƒ}$[<font color=\"silver\">â€¦](https://qiita.com/ironball/items/6acb3546312f4c65ec54)</font></font><br>\n","<img src=\"https://camo.qiitausercontent.com/4b2a8b68fcf74c56350ef368cdbc7b5e4ef73f2e/68747470733a2f2f71696974612d696d6167652d73746f72652e73332e61702d6e6f727468656173742d312e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f302f3438383537372f35333564336439302d343035302d313862392d316263372d3465373066346666623233322e706e67\" width=\"480\"><br><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\">$\\tiny\\text{ç”»åƒå¼•ç”¨å…ƒ}$[<font color=\"silver\">â€¦](https://www.xiaowenying.com/machine-learning/2019/11/18/svm.html)</font><br>\n","<img src=\"https://www.xiaowenying.com/assets/post_img/svm/7824BB24CA8355AFBD5B9BF42521096D.jpg\" width=\"320\"><br><br>\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"TrPXhicbAnyW"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["####<font color=\"silver\">ã‚ªãƒƒã‚ºæ¯”</font>\n","- <font color=\"silver\">ç¢ºç‡, $\\quad 0 < p(x) < 1$</font><br><br>\n","ç™ºç”Ÿç¢ºç‡$p$, ç™ºç”Ÿã—ãªã„ç¢ºç‡$1-p$<br><br>\n","- 