ack\">$\\sqrt {\\dfrac {2}{n}},\\quad\\displaystyle \\sqrt \\frac{2}{n1}$ã‚’æ¨™æº–åå·®ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã‚¬ã‚¦ã‚¹åˆ†å¸ƒ<br><br>\n","n1ï¼š<font color=\"silver\">å‰ã®å±¤ã®ãƒãƒ¼ãƒ‰æ•°</font><br>"],"metadata":{"id":"Hq5eruwsO6_Y"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["####<font color=\"silver\">WeightDecay</font>\n","l2_loss = l2_loss + torch.norm(w) ** 2<br>\n","l1_loss = l1_loss + torch.norm(w, 1)<br><br> \n","$\\displaystyle L = L' + \\frac{1}{2} \\lambda \\sum_{l=1}^{layers} \\sum_{i, ~~j} (w_{ij}^{l})^2$<br>  \n","$\\displaystyle \\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial {\\bf W}_t} = \\frac{\\partial L'}{\\partial {\\bf W}_t} + \\lambda {\\bf W}_{t}$<br>  \n","$\\bf W$ :  <font color=\"silver\">é‡ã¿è¡Œåˆ—  </font><br>$w_{i,j}^l$ :<font color=\"silver\"> $l$å±¤ç›®ã®é‡ã¿è¡Œåˆ—${\\bf W}$ã®$i, j $æˆåˆ†<br></font>\n","$L$ :<font color=\"silver\"> æ­£å‰‡åŒ–é …ã‚’åŠ ãˆãŸå¾Œã®æå¤±<br></font>\n","$L'$ : <font color=\"silver\">æ­£å‰‡åŒ–é …ã‚’åŠ ãˆã‚‹å‰ã®æå¤± <br></font>\n","$layers$ :<font color=\"silver\"> å±¤ç•ªå·<br></font>\n","$\\lambda$ :<font color=\"silver\"> ä¿‚æ•°<br></font><br>\n","<font color=\"silver\"># æå¤±ã®è£œæ­£</font><br>\n","weight_decayÂ =Â 0<br>\n","forÂ idxÂ inÂ range(1,Â self.hidden_layer_numÂ +Â 2):<br>\n","$\\qquad$WÂ =Â self.params['W'Â +Â str(idx)]<br>\n","$\\qquad$weight_decayÂ +=Â 0.5Â *Â lmdÂ *Â np.sum(W**2)Â <font color=\"silver\">Â #Â å…¨ã¦ã®è¡Œåˆ—Wã«ã¤ã„ã¦ç©ç®—ã—ã¦ã„ã</font><br>\n","returnÂ self.lastLayer.forward(y,Â t)Â +Â weight_decayÂ <br>\n","<font color=\"silver\"># å‹¾é…ã®è£œæ­£</font><br>\n","gradsÂ =Â {}<br>\n","forÂ idxÂ inÂ range(1,Â self.hidden_layer_num+2):<br>\n","$\\qquad$grads['W'Â +Â str(idx)]Â =Â self.layers['Affine'Â +Â str(idx)].dWÂ +Â lmdÂ *Â self.layers['Affine'Â +Â str(idx)].W<br>\n","$\\qquad$grads['b'Â +Â str(idx)]Â =Â self.layers['Affine'Â +Â str(idx)].db<br>\n","returnÂ grads<br>"],"metadata":{"id":"c3cuHpl6Nkbi"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### <font color=\"silver\">å‹¾é…ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒãƒ”ãƒ³ã‚°</font>\n","torch.nn.utils.clip_grad_norm